                "expert": "The Bombardment mage can maintain peak firing performance for roughly a week with minimal rest. The device manages all biological needs, drawing supplemental energy from ambient mana when caloric reserves run dry. Extended bombardment campaigns, week-long siege operations, and back-to-back fire missions are all viable. The Bombardment mage simply does not stop unless they choose to.\n\nOpponents who face this enhancement quickly recognize the dramatic difference in sustained bombardment capability across long engagements. The ranged specialist who internalizes this advantage suppresses the bombardment exchange with growing confidence.",
                "master": "Operational endurance approaches the practical ceiling of what a Bombardment mage's body and device can sustain. The mage can maintain peak targeting performance indefinitely while mana holds, with no meaningful degradation in accuracy, reaction speed, or firing discipline. Extended bombardment operations that would exhaust entire artillery crews become routine. The Bombardment mage is the last one firing — always.\n\nA bombardment platform with this enhancement operates at a unmatched advantage in sustained bombardment capability across long engagements. Where an unaugmented ranged specialist must account for limitations, the enhanced mage treats artillery operations as territory to be controlled rather than endured."
