                "apprentice": "The mana sheath thickens, providing meaningful protection against blast force transmitted through the torso. The Bombardment mage can survive near-misses from heavy ordnance without lethal organ damage. The device adds a warning system that alerts the mage when their vitals are being targeted by counter-battery.\n\nThe continuing fire even after taking hits this provides changes the fundamental rhythm of fire-direction. Each engagement flows more efficiently, and the cumulative effect across a full engagement is marked.",
