                "expert": "The Bombardment mage's gravity manipulation is sophisticated enough to shift between extreme states mid-operation. A repositioning dash begins light for impossible speed and the firing stance arrives heavy for absolute stability. The mage can fight in low-gravity or high-gravity environments without adaptation.\n\nThe rapid repositioning for optimal firing solutions this provides changes the fundamental rhythm of fire-direction. Each volley flows more efficiently, and the cumulative effect across a full engagement is dramatic.",
                "master": "With Ballistic Reposition fully realized, the Bombardment mage's artillery effectiveness approaches its practical ceiling. The Bombardment mage shifts gravity states with zero transition time, making every reposition a gravity-assisted tactical movement. The mage can relocate to any firing position in a gravity-reduced dash and arrive in a gravity-amplified immovable stance — mobility and stability combined with impossible grace.\n\nThe transcendent improvement in rapid repositioning for optimal firing solutions reshapes how the artillery mage approaches ranged combat. The ranged engagement shifts as the ranged specialist establishes fire-superiority that compounds with every volleys."
