                "expert": "The Bombardment mage's reflexive dodges approach the practical ceiling of artillery evasion. Every incoming counter-battery attack is met with the optimal evasive response — minimal movement, maximum effectiveness, immediate return-fire position. The mage dodges as efficiently as they fire, wasting no motion and losing no targeting data.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the overwhelming improvement in automatic evasion of counter-battery fire is difficult to overstate. The ranged specialist who masters this enhancement outranges ranged combat with an authority that shifts the balance of every fire-mission.",
                "master": "Counter-Battery Evasion operates at the highest practical level of bombardment augmentation. The Bombardment mage's body evades incoming attacks with near-zero latency and near-zero wasted motion. Every dodge flows into an optimal firing position, and the mage operates with the certainty that no counter-battery fire will find its mark unless it is simply too fast and too numerous to evade.\n\nThe returns from long-range capability scale progressively through sustained artillery operations. An early unmatched edge widens as the engagement continues, and the fire-support who endures longest commands most completely."
