                "master": "Mastery of Barrage Synchronization elevates the Bombardment mage's fire to its most formidable expression. The Bombardment mage creates a fire team that functions as a single artillery system — every member aware of every target, every firing solution, and every defensive state. The mage leads this formation with perfect synchronization, making their team more than the sum of its parts in bombardment combat.\n\nThe enhancement to coordinated fire that maximizes ranged impact transforms the artillery mage's approach to long-range fighting. What begins as a transcendent advantage in isolated salvos becomes a systemic shift across the entire engagement."
