                "expert": "Sub-munition splitting becomes standard. The Bombardment mage can fragment a single plasma round into multiple guided projectiles mid-flight, engaging dispersed targets simultaneously. Sustained bombardment mode allows continuous fire — one round every fraction of a second — for as long as mana reserves hold. The device handles all trajectory calculations autonomously.\n\nThis improvement to area-denial fire that controls the ranged battlefield adds tactical depth to every salvo within the bombardment exchange. The artillery mage gains options that unenhanced practitioners simply do not have, and each additional option represents a dramatic expansion of their combat repertoire.",
                "master": "In the Bombardment mage's hands, Artillery Flame reaches the pinnacle of ranged application. The Bombardment mage achieves near-perfect thermal compression efficiency, and the sub-munition system can split rounds into up to eight guided fragments with independent targeting. A sustained barrage can demolish a fortified position within minutes.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the transcendent improvement in bombardment capability is difficult to overstate. The bombardment platform who masters this enhancement outranges ranged combat with an authority that shifts the balance of every fire-mission."
