                "master": "In the Bombardment mage's hands, Cyclone Shell reaches the pinnacle of ranged application. The Bombardment mage fires devastating gravitational rounds that create inescapable vortices at range. No cover is safe, no position is stable, and no opponent can maintain footing in the Bombardment mage's zone of gravitational control.\n\nOpponents who face this enhancement quickly recognize the extraordinary difference in pulling vortex that drags enemies out of cover. The bombardment platform who internalizes this advantage dictates the bombardment exchange with growing confidence."
