                "expert": "The Bombardment mage's Storm Barrage creates devastating controlled weather that makes the entire target area hostile. Wind, rain, and lightning serve the bombardment — opponents are buffeted, blinded, and struck by environmental violence while the Bombardment mage fires with storm-enhanced precision. The mage is the storm's architect — their bombardment is the storm's fury.\n\nThe substantial gains in bombardment capability create momentum that is difficult to arrest. Each successful barrage in long-range fighting makes the next one easier, and the bombardment platform who seizes the initiative early controls the engagement from that point forward.",
                "master": "Full mastery of Storm Barrage transforms the Bombardment mage into a devastating artillery force. The Bombardment mage fires devastating weather rounds that create massive controlled storms over the target area. Wind, rain, and lightning serve the Bombardment mage's fire — opponents are overwhelmed by environmental violence while the mage fires with storm-enhanced precision. The mage is the storm given purpose — their bombardment is the weather's weapon.\n\nThe transcendent improvement in weather artillery that strikes across the entire engagement range reshapes how the fire-support approaches ranged combat. Each volley demonstrates the bombardment platform establishes fire-superiority that compounds with every engagements."
