                "master": "Gravity Anchor reaches its combat apex, and the Bombardment mage's fire benefits from maximum augmentation. The Bombardment mage fires devastating gravity rounds that create inescapable gravitational wells at range. Opponents are pinned in place, unable to move, unable to escape, and the Bombardment mage's fire is devastating against immobile targets. The mage is a walking singularity — their bombardment creates zones where nothing moves and everything dies.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the transcendent improvement in artillery capability is difficult to overstate. The ranged specialist who masters this enhancement outranges ranged combat with an authority that shifts the balance of every fire-mission."
