                "master": "The Bombardment mage who has fully mastered Mag-Storm Salvo fires at the height of ranged capability. The Bombardment mage fires devastating magnetic rounds that make all metal equipment a liability. The mage's bombardment turns opponents' weapons, armor, and tools against them — iron and steel serve only the Bombardment mage in the magnetic storm zone.\n\nThe transcendent improvement in long-range capability reshapes how the fire-support approaches ranged combat. Each volley demonstrates the bombardment platform establishes fire-superiority that compounds with every engagements."
