                "adept": "Professional-grade mental defense for artillery operations. The Bombardment mage's mind becomes a fortress of targeting clarity — psychic attacks are deflected by the same focus that guides their fire. The screen extends a protective aura to nearby fire-team members, providing them basic mental defense during coordinated bombardment.\n\nOpponents who face this enhancement quickly recognize the clear difference in psychic hardening that maintains fire-direction against mental assault. The bombardment platform who internalizes this advantage controls the bombardment exchange with growing confidence.",
                "expert": "The Bombardment mage's Counter-Intel Screen approaches the practical ceiling of artillery-oriented mental defense. Psychic attacks that would disrupt targeting glance off the mage's combat-hardened mind. The mental fortress is so deeply integrated with fire-direction that the Bombardment mage maintains total targeting clarity regardless of psychic pressure.\n\nOpponents who face this enhancement quickly recognize the dramatic difference in psychic hardening that maintains fire-direction against mental assault. The bombardment platform who internalizes this advantage suppresses the bombardment exchange with growing confidence.",
                "master": "At this level, Counter-Intel Screen is the Bombardment mage's cannon made manifest — fire-direction and spell are indistinguishable. The Bombardment mage's mind is a formidable fortress of targeting clarity — few psychic forces can disrupt the focus that guides their fire. The mage maintains near-perfect targeting accuracy regardless of mental pressure.\n\nA ranged specialist with this enhancement operates at a unmatched advantage in psychic hardening that maintains fire-direction against mental assault. Where an unaugmented bombardment platform must account for limitations, the enhanced mage treats artillery operations as territory to be controlled rather than endured."
