                "expert": "The Bombardment mage's targeting prophecy approaches the practical ceiling of artillery precognition. The mage perceives the next several seconds of the battlefield with extraordinary clarity, making every opponent's movement predictable and every bombardment devastatingly accurate. The mage fires with the certainty of someone who has already won — because they have seen the impacts before they occur.\n\nThe substantial gains in predictive fire-direction that places ordnance where enemies will be create momentum that is difficult to arrest. Each successful bombardment in long-range fighting makes the next one easier, and the bombardment platform who seizes the initiative early suppresses the engagement from that point forward.",
                "master": "With targeting prophecy fully realized, the Bombardment mage's artillery effectiveness approaches its practical ceiling. The Bombardment mage perceives the flow of combat before it happens, making every opponent's movement predictable and every bombardment devastatingly accurate. The mage fires with absolute certainty — their rounds are always where they need to be because they have already seen where they need to be.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the transcendent improvement in predictive fire-direction that places ordnance where enemies will be is difficult to overstate. The ranged specialist who masters this enhancement dominates ranged combat with an authority that shifts the balance of every barrage."
