                "apprentice": "The direct manifestation becomes more refined, allowing the Bombardment mage to will bombardment into existence with reduced mana cost. The bypass of device computation provides faster fire activation at the cost of mana efficiency, giving the Bombardment mage emergency speed options when split-second timing matters.\n\nThe willed destruction that manifests artillery from thought alone this provides changes the fundamental rhythm of fire-direction. Each engagement flows more efficiently, and the cumulative effect across a full engagement is marked.",
                "adept": "Professional-grade direct manifestation for artillery operations. The Bombardment mage can will bombardment into existence with reasonable efficiency, bypassing device computation for instant activation. The technique provides a crucial speed advantage in engagements where milliseconds determine whether fire arrives in time.\n\nThis improvement to ranged capability adds tactical depth to every salvo within the bombardment exchange. The artillery mage gains options that unenhanced practitioners simply do not have, and each additional option represents a clear expansion of their combat repertoire.",
                "expert": "The Bombardment mage's direct manifestation approaches the practical ceiling of fire-direction will-to-action. The mage can will bombardment into existence with near-zero delay, bypassing device computation entirely. The technique makes the Bombardment mage terrifyingly responsive — fire manifests the instant the mage wills it, with no processing delay between intent and bombardment.\n\nThe formidable enhancement to willed destruction that manifests artillery from thought alone converts uncertainty into calculated risk. In fire-direction, the bombardment platform who can rely on this advantage makes decisions faster and commits with greater conviction than any opponent who must second-guess.",
                "master": "Full mastery of direct manifestation transforms the Bombardment mage into a devastating artillery force. The Bombardment mage wills bombardment into existence with devastating efficiency and near-zero delay. The mage is a weapon of pure will — their fire manifests the instant they think it, with no delay, no computation, and no barrier between intent and bombardment.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the transcendent improvement in willed destruction that manifests artillery from thought alone is difficult to overstate. The ranged specialist who masters this enhancement commands ranged combat with an authority that shifts the balance of every bombardment."
