                "expert": "The Bombardment mage's Ordnance Ascension approaches the practical ceiling of bombardment transcendent enhancement. All bombardment capabilities are enhanced dramatically — targeting, fire-direction, accuracy, endurance, and mana efficiency operate beyond normal limits. The Bombardment mage fights as something more than human — their fire carries the weight of transcendent enhancement that makes every aspect of bombardment devastatingly effective.\n\nThe enhancement to ranged capability transforms the artillery mage's approach to long-range fighting. What begins as a overwhelming advantage in isolated engagements becomes a systemic shift across the entire engagement.",
                "master": "Ordnance Ascension reaches its combat apex, and the Bombardment mage's fire benefits from maximum augmentation. The Bombardment mage achieves devastating transcendent enhancement that elevates all bombardment capabilities beyond normal limits. The mage is a transcendent artillery platform — their fire carries the weight of enhanced targeting, accuracy, endurance, and mana efficiency simultaneously. The Bombardment mage is the practical ceiling of what an artillery combatant can become through transcendent enhancement — their fire the instrument of a warrior who has transcended normal limits entirely.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the transcendent improvement in elevated state that maximizes ranged output beyond conventional limits is difficult to overstate. The ranged specialist who masters this enhancement commands ranged combat with an authority that shifts the balance of every bombardment."
