                "adept": "The Thaumaturge's skeleton is reinforced to support-grade standards. The mage can perform demanding rescue operations — breaking through walls, lifting heavy debris, carrying multiple casualties — without risk of bone injury. Minor damage from sustained physical operations repairs during pauses.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the pronounced improvement in physical durability that keeps the formation intact is difficult to overstate. The support mage who masters this enhancement stabilizes support operations with an authority that shifts the balance of every healing pulse.",
