                "master": "The Thaumaturge's bones are effectively unbreakable by any physical force encountered in rescue operations. The reinforcement is permanent, maintaining peak structural integrity through any support operation. The Thaumaturge performs rescue without fear of bone injury — their skeleton is as reliable as their commitment to their team.\n\nA formation anchor with this enhancement operates at a unmatched advantage in physical durability that keeps the formation intact. Where an unaugmented triage specialist must account for limitations, the enhanced mage treats formation fighting as territory to be controlled rather than endured."
