                "expert": "The mana barrier around vital organs is thick enough to stop most attacks that reach the support position. The Thaumaturge can maintain healing and buffing through sustained combat without concern for internal injury. The protection extends to the brain, guarding against concussive force from nearby explosions.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the overwhelming improvement in staying operational to keep healing the formation is difficult to overstate. The support mage who masters this enhancement stabilizes support operations with an authority that shifts the balance of every healing pulse.",
                "master": "With Vital organ protection fully realized, the Thaumaturge's support effectiveness approaches its practical ceiling. The Thaumaturge's organs are shielded by a permanent, adaptive mana barrier that disperses damage and regenerates faster than most threats can deplete it. The support mage can sustain combat operations that would be lethal to unprotected medics and continue supporting their team.\n\nThe peerless enhancement to staying operational to keep healing the formation converts uncertainty into calculated risk. In triage situations, the healer who can rely on this advantage makes decisions faster and commits with greater conviction than any opponent who must second-guess."
