                "expert": "Adrenaline surges are continuous and precisely controlled. The Thaumaturge operates at peak support intensity indefinitely, the device providing a perfectly calibrated flow of combat-enhancing hormones. Fear and hesitation are functionally eliminated — the mage supports with absolute commitment to every healing and buff action.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the overwhelming improvement in critical-triage speed when the formation is under strain is difficult to overstate. The support mage who masters this enhancement stabilizes support operations with an authority that shifts the balance of every healing pulse.",
                "master": "The Thaumaturge's adrenal system is permanently optimized for support operations. Every moment is peak support readiness. The mage operates with maximum urgency and minimum waste, their body a perfectly calibrated support platform that never tires, never hesitates, and never gives up on a teammate.\n\nThe peerless enhancement to critical-triage speed when the formation is under strain converts uncertainty into calculated risk. In triage situations, the healer who can rely on this advantage makes decisions faster and commits with greater conviction than any opponent who must second-guess."
