                "expert": "The bond approaches its theoretical maximum. The device is a true extension of the Thaumaturge's will — it processes support routines as thought processes, with no perceptible delay between intention and effect. The mage can manipulate the device remotely with fine control, accessing any ritual or reference instantly.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the overwhelming improvement in device integration that streamlines support delivery is difficult to overstate. The support mage who masters this enhancement sustains support operations with an authority that shifts the balance of every healing pulse.",
                "master": "The Focus Bond is complete. Thaumaturge and device are one — the grimoire is as natural as a thought, as responsive as an instinct, and as reliable as the mage's own heartbeat. The device can be reshaped mid-combat through the bond, and the mage supports with absolute certainty that their rituals will be exactly where they need to be.\n\nThe peerless enhancement to device integration that streamlines support delivery converts uncertainty into calculated risk. In triage situations, the healer who can rely on this advantage makes decisions faster and commits with greater conviction than any opponent who must second-guess."
