                "master": "The Thaumaturge maintains comprehensive support awareness at all times. Every ally's status, every buff's duration, every injury's severity within operational range is perceived and processed in real time. The Thaumaturge cannot miss a teammate in need, cannot overlook a fading buff, and cannot fail to notice a developing crisis.\n\nA formation anchor with this enhancement operates at a unmatched advantage in formation-wide awareness for optimal support placement. Where an unaugmented triage specialist must account for limitations, the enhanced mage treats formation fighting as territory to be controlled rather than endured."
