                "expert": "Impact absorption approaches its theoretical maximum. The Thaumaturge can withstand significant combat damage while maintaining continuous support. The device efficiently converts absorbed force, making the mage increasingly resilient through extended operations where interruptions would normally accumulate.\n\nAllies who receive this support quickly benefit from the dramatic difference in enduring attacks while maintaining the healing rotation. The triage specialist who internalizes this advantage bolsters the healing rotation with growing confidence.",
                "master": "The Thaumaturge absorbs impact force with near-optimal efficiency. Attacks that would interrupt support casting in lesser mages are shrugged off, and the mage can sustain continuous support operations with minimal concern for physical disruption. The spell operates permanently, ensuring uninterrupted support.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the transcendent improvement in enduring attacks while maintaining the healing rotation is difficult to overstate. The support mage who masters this enhancement anchors support operations with an authority that shifts the balance of every healing pulse."
