                "master": "Mastery of Thaumaturge's recovery elevates the Thaumaturge's support to its most formidable expression. Physical damage is repaired with remarkable efficiency, and the mage approaches full support readiness between operations faster than any unaugmented medic could achieve with weeks of rest. The Thaumaturge is always ready for the next support rotation.\n\nA formation anchor with this enhancement operates at a unmatched advantage in formation capability. Where an unaugmented triage specialist must account for limitations, the enhanced mage treats formation fighting as territory to be controlled rather than endured."
