                "beginner": "The Thaumaturge's body gains basic resistance to toxins commonly encountered in field operations — chemical agents, contaminated environments, and biological hazards. The device filters common toxins before they can impair support casting or diagnostic accuracy.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the noticeable improvement in uninterrupted support despite toxic battlefield conditions is difficult to overstate. The support mage who masters this enhancement stabilizes support operations with an authority that shifts the balance of every healing pulse.",
