                "expert": "The Thaumaturge is effectively immune to all known field toxins. The device identifies and neutralizes novel agents nearly instantly, and the mage can maintain peak support performance through contaminated environments that would kill unaugmented operators. The mage can enter hazardous zones to rescue allies without personal risk.\n\nAllies who receive this support quickly benefit from the dramatic difference in uninterrupted support despite toxic battlefield conditions. The triage specialist who internalizes this advantage reinforces the healing rotation with growing confidence.",
                "master": "In the Thaumaturge's hands, Toxin resistance reaches the pinnacle of support application. The Thaumaturge's body neutralizes any toxin before it can affect support performance. The mage operates without concern for environmental threats in any support scenario — the perfect field medic who can reach any ally in any condition.\n\nA formation anchor with this enhancement operates at a unmatched advantage in uninterrupted support despite toxic battlefield conditions. Where an unaugmented triage specialist must account for limitations, the enhanced mage treats formation fighting as territory to be controlled rather than endured."
