                "adept": "Professional-grade equilibrium for support operations. The Thaumaturge can maintain perfect balance during the most demanding support sequences — complex ritual gestures, rapid triage movements, and physical rescue operations. The device corrects balance faster than conscious thought.\n\nAllies who receive this support quickly benefit from the clear difference in unshakeable grounding during support operations. The triage specialist who internalizes this advantage reinforces the healing rotation with growing confidence.",
                "expert": "The Thaumaturge's balance approaches the practical ceiling for support operations. Any surface that can physically support the mage is viable for ritual casting. The mage can perform emergency medicine on a rolling ship's deck or while being carried by allies without compromising support precision.\n\nThe substantial gains in unshakeable grounding during support operations create momentum that is difficult to arrest. Each successful ward rotation in sustained engagements makes the next one easier, and the coordination hub who seizes the initiative early reinforces the engagement from that point forward.",
                "master": "The Thaumaturge's equilibrium is permanently optimized for support operations. Balance is maintained through any physical challenge — the mage supports as effectively in a collapsing building as on solid ground. No combat condition can disrupt this mage's ritual stability.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the transcendent improvement in unshakeable grounding during support operations is difficult to overstate. The support mage who masters this enhancement anchors support operations with an authority that shifts the balance of every healing pulse."
