                "adept": "Professional-grade mass modulation for support operations. The Thaumaturge can double their effective mass for an interruption-resistant support stance or halve it for rapid ally-to-ally movement. The transitions are fast enough to shift within a single support rotation.\n\nThe mass management for optimal support positioning this provides changes the fundamental rhythm of triage situations. Each triage round flows more efficiently, and the cumulative effect across a full engagement is clear.",
