                "master": "Full mastery of Mass modulation transforms the Thaumaturge into a devastating support force. The Thaumaturge can shift between extreme mass states with zero transition time — light for reaching allies, heavy for stable support, shifting at the perfect moment. Impossible stability combined with impossible mobility.\n\nThe transcendent improvement in mass management for optimal support positioning reshapes how the support mage approaches support operations. The formation holds stronger as the formation anchor establishes formation integrity that compounds with every healing pulses."
