                "expert": "The Thaumaturge's blood manipulation provides comprehensive control over circulatory systems — both their own and those of nearby allies. Wounds are sealed with remarkable speed, blood pressure is maintained through severe trauma, and the mage can stabilize allies who would otherwise bleed out during combat.\n\nThe substantial gains in blood as a resource for extended support delivery create momentum that is difficult to arrest. Each successful ward rotation in sustained engagements makes the next one easier, and the coordination hub who seizes the initiative early fortifies the engagement from that point forward.",
                "master": "Blood manipulation reaches its support apex, and the Thaumaturge's healing benefits from maximum augmentation. The Thaumaturge's circulatory control extends to both themselves and nearby allies — wounds seal almost instantly, blood pressure remains stable through any trauma, and the mage can sustain support operations regardless of personal or allied injury. The ultimate field medic whose control over life's vital fluid saves lives as surely as any healing spell.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the transcendent improvement in blood as a resource for extended support delivery is difficult to overstate. The support mage who masters this enhancement sustains support operations with an authority that shifts the balance of every healing pulse."
