                "expert": "The Thaumaturge's support instinct approaches the practical ceiling of ally awareness. Every teammate's condition, intention, and need is perceived through an intuitive framework that processes support data faster than conscious thought. The mage supports with the certainty of a guardian who knows exactly when and where their protection is needed.\n\nThe intuitive triage that anticipates formation needs this provides changes the fundamental rhythm of triage situations. Each triage round flows more efficiently, and the cumulative effect across a full engagement is dramatic.",
                "master": "The Thaumaturge who has fully mastered Custodian's Instinct supports at the height of formation capability. Support awareness is so refined that the Thaumaturge perceives every ally need and threat as clearly as physical sensation. The mage knows who needs healing, who needs buffs, who needs protection with absolute certainty — their support guided by an instinct that never fails.\n\nThe intuitive triage that anticipates formation needs this provides changes the fundamental rhythm of triage situations. Each triage round flows more efficiently, and the cumulative effect across a full engagement is extraordinary."
