                "master": "Mastery of Precision Lance elevates the Thaumaturge's support to its most formidable expression. The Thaumaturge wields a surgical instrument of extraordinary precision — cauterizing any wound, removing any damage, and delivering targeted treatment with exceptional accuracy. The mage is a walking surgeon whose precision exceeds any conventional medical technology, making any injury treatable in the field.\n\nThis elemental support creates advantages in every triage cycle Every spell carries the element's signature; every heal delivers the element's consequence; every support action demonstrates that the Thaumaturge and the element are not allies but a single unified healing force. The mage is the element's vessel, and the vessel never runs dry."
