                "expert": "The Thaumaturge's Resonant Pulse operates as a comprehensive medical and defensive tool. The vibrations treat any internal injury, stimulate dramatic healing, and create a protective sonic field that makes the formation harder to hit. The mage is a walking diagnostic and treatment system — their pulse reaches injuries that no other treatment can access.\n\nThe substantial gains in harmonic frequencies that promote cellular regeneration in allies create momentum that is difficult to arrest. Each successful ward rotation in sustained engagements makes the next one easier, and the coordination hub who seizes the initiative early bolsters the engagement from that point forward.",
                "master": "Resonant Pulse operates at the highest practical level of support augmentation. The Thaumaturge creates a comprehensive sonic support system that treats any internal injury, stimulates extraordinary healing, and protects the formation with a deflective sonic field. The mage is a walking medical resonator — their pulse heals from within and protects from without, making any injury treatable and any attack easier to weather.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the transcendent improvement in harmonic frequencies that promote cellular regeneration in allies is difficult to overstate. The support mage who masters this enhancement stabilizes support operations with an authority that shifts the balance of every healing pulse."
