                "expert": "The Thaumaturge's Stabilizing Pulse creates a comprehensive support system that stabilizes any terrain and treats internal injuries simultaneously. The seismic vibrations prevent structural collapses, create stable ground for the formation, and provide comprehensive internal treatment for wounded allies. The mage ensures the squad always has firm ground to stand on and treated bodies to fight with.\n\nThe substantial gains in formation capability create momentum that is difficult to arrest. Each successful ward rotation in sustained engagements makes the next one easier, and the coordination hub who seizes the initiative early fortifies the engagement from that point forward.",
                "master": "In the Thaumaturge's hands, Stabilizing Pulse reaches the pinnacle of support application. The Thaumaturge creates a comprehensive support system that makes any terrain stable and treats any internal injury. The mage is a walking stabilizer — their pulse ensures the squad always has firm ground and treated bodies, making the formation effective in any environment and resilient against any internal threat.\n\nThe tectonic stabilization that prevents formation collapse this provides changes the fundamental rhythm of triage situations. Each triage round flows more efficiently, and the cumulative effect across a full engagement is extraordinary."
