                "expert": "The Thaumaturge's Aegis of Will approaches the practical ceiling of support-oriented mental defense. The shield protects the entire formation from psychic intrusion, and the Thaumaturge can maintain total support clarity regardless of mental pressure. The shield extends to all allies in operational range, making the formation nearly immune to psychic disruption.\n\nThe substantial gains in thought-barrier that protects the formation's mental coordination create momentum that is difficult to arrest. Each successful ward rotation in sustained engagements makes the next one easier, and the coordination hub who seizes the initiative early fortifies the engagement from that point forward.",
                "master": "At this level, Aegis of Will is the Thaumaturge's healing made manifest — support and spell are indistinguishable. The Thaumaturge creates a comprehensive mental defense that protects the entire formation from psychic intrusion. The mage is a walking mental fortress — their shield ensures the squad fights with total mental clarity, making psychic attacks against the formation nearly useless.\n\nFrom a tactical perspective, the transcendent improvement in thought-barrier that protects the formation's mental coordination is difficult to overstate. The support mage who masters this enhancement sustains support operations with an authority that shifts the balance of every healing pulse."
