                "adept": "Professional-grade emergency teleportation for support operations. The Thaumaturge can Emergency Extract allies from any danger, teleport themselves to any position for emergency healing, and reposition the formation to avoid threats. The technique makes the Thaumaturge's support reach effectively boundless — no ally is too far to save.\n\nThe spatial relocation for rapid formation adjustment and emergency extraction this provides changes the fundamental rhythm of triage situations. Each triage round flows more efficiently, and the cumulative effect across a full engagement is clear.",
                "expert": "The Thaumaturge's Emergency Extraction approaches the practical ceiling of support teleportation. The mage can teleport any ally to safety from any position, and teleport themselves to any endangered teammate for immediate support. The technique makes the Thaumaturge's support range near-absolute — no ally is beyond rescue, no wound is beyond treatment.\n\nThe enhancement to spatial relocation for rapid formation adjustment and emergency extraction transforms the coordination hub's approach to sustained engagements. What begins as a overwhelming advantage in isolated ward rotations becomes a systemic shift across the entire engagement.",
                "master": "Emergency Extraction operates at the peak of support enhancement — the Thaumaturge's formation capability is dramatically elevated. The Thaumaturge can teleport any ally to safety or teleport themselves to any endangered teammate instantly. The mage is a walking rescue system — their teleportation ensures no ally is ever beyond saving, making the formation nearly extremely difficult to isolate or defeat through positional advantage.\n\nThe spatial relocation for rapid formation adjustment and emergency extraction this provides changes the fundamental rhythm of triage situations. Each triage round flows more efficiently, and the cumulative effect across a full engagement is extraordinary."
