                "beginner": "The Thaumaturge bestows the Sacrament — a minor combat blessing on nearby allies that enhances their resilience and fighting spirit. The blessing is weak but provides a noticeable edge in combat survivability, making allies slightly harder to wound.\n\nThe blessing-enhanced support that amplifies the formation's capabilities this provides changes the fundamental rhythm of triage situations. Each triage round flows more efficiently, and the cumulative effect across a full engagement is discernible.",
