                "expert": "The Thaumaturge's Sacrament approaches the practical ceiling of support enhancement. Every blessed ally fights at significantly enhanced capability — their resilience is improved, their stamina is extended, and their morale is elevated. The Thaumaturge can bless an entire formation, creating a unit of devastatingly effective warriors.\n\nThe blessing-enhanced support that amplifies the formation's capabilities this provides changes the fundamental rhythm of triage situations. Each triage round flows more efficiently, and the cumulative effect across a full engagement is dramatic.",
                "master": "Full mastery of Sacrament transforms the Thaumaturge into a devastating support force. The Thaumaturge bestows devastating enhancements that make every blessed ally significantly more effective. The mage is a walking blessing — their presence elevates the entire formation, making every ally more resilient, more enduring, and more effective in combat.\n\nThe transcendent improvement in blessing-enhanced support that amplifies the formation's capabilities reshapes how the support mage approaches support operations. Every healing cycle reinforces the formation anchor establishes formation integrity that compounds with every healing pulses."
