                "expert": "The Thaumaturge's Guardian Spirits approach the practical ceiling of support summoning. Multiple powerful protective entities provide comprehensive defensive support for the formation, intercepting attacks, raising barriers, and providing advance warning of threats. The Thaumaturge creates a spiritual escort that makes the formation dramatically harder to assault.\n\nThis improvement to conjured support spirits that extend healing reach across the formation adds tactical depth to every formation adjustment within the healing rotation. The triage specialist gains options that unenhanced practitioners simply do not have, and each additional option represents a dramatic expansion of their combat repertoire.",
                "master": "Guardian Summoning reaches its support apex, and the Thaumaturge's healing benefits from maximum augmentation. The Thaumaturge summons devastating protective entities that provide comprehensive defensive support for the entire formation. The mage is a walking spiritual escort — their guardians ensure the squad is always protected, always warned, and always supported by an array of powerful protective spirits.\n\nThe returns from conjured support spirits that extend healing reach across the formation scale progressively through sustained formation fighting. An early unmatched edge widens as the engagement continues, and the formation anchor who endures longest sustains most completely."
