                "expert": "The Thaumaturge's Diagnostic Empathy approaches the practical ceiling of support emotional insight. Every ally's emotional state is clearly readable, and the Thaumaturge exploits every insight to deliver optimally targeted support. The mage fights with the certainty of someone who knows exactly which ally needs what — and delivers it with remarkable precision.\n\nA formation anchor with this enhancement operates at a decisive advantage in formation capability. Where an unaugmented triage specialist must account for limitations, the enhanced mage treats formation fighting as territory to be controlled rather than endured.",
                "master": "In the Thaumaturge's hands, Diagnostic Empathy reaches the pinnacle of support application. The Thaumaturge reads allies' emotional states with absolute clarity, understanding their psychological needs completely. The mage is a walking diagnostic system — their empathy ensures every support action is perfectly targeted, making the formation's psychological and physical care optimally efficient.\n\nAllies who receive this support quickly benefit from the extraordinary difference in triage capability. The triage specialist who internalizes this advantage bolsters the healing rotation with growing confidence."
