                "apprentice": "The true sight deepens, revealing hidden magical effects, disguised threats, and concealed conditions that would escape normal observation. The Thaumaturge can see through illusions that might deceive teammates, ensuring their support addresses real rather than apparent conditions. The technique makes deceptive threats useless against the Thaumaturge's diagnostic capability.\n\nThis improvement to healing capability adds tactical depth to every formation adjustment within the healing rotation. The triage specialist gains options that unenhanced practitioners simply do not have, and each additional option represents a marked expansion of their combat repertoire.",
