                "expert": "The Thaumaturge's fate manipulation approaches the practical ceiling of formation protection. The mage can ensure that critical combat outcomes consistently favor the formation. Probability itself becomes the Thaumaturge's ally — their influence makes the squad extremely difficult to defeat through a single devastating blow, as fate consistently intervenes in the formation's favor.\n\nThe overwhelming improvement in support capability reshapes how the support mage approaches support operations. Every healing cycle reinforces the formation anchor establishes formation integrity that compounds with every healing pulses.",
                "master": "fate manipulation operates at the peak of support enhancement — the Thaumaturge's formation capability is dramatically elevated. The Thaumaturge influences combat probability with devastating consistency in the formation's favor, ensuring critical outcomes consistently protect the squad. The mage is fate's guardian — their influence makes the formation remarkably difficult to defeat, as probability consistently bends toward the squad's survival.\n\nThe enhancement to support capability transforms the coordination hub's approach to sustained engagements. What begins as a transcendent advantage in isolated ward rotations becomes a systemic shift across the entire engagement."
